Package it.polimi.ingsw.utils

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Observer
    The method Observer.update(String) of the classes with this interface will be called when the class they're observing notify them.
    Originator
    The Originator class can produce snapshots of its own state with Originator.createMemento(), as well as restore its state from snapshots when needed with Originator.restore(Object).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CareTaker
    A caretaker can request a memento from the originator (to save its internal state) through the method CareTaker.save(Originator) and pass a memento back to the originator (to restore to a previous state) through the method CareTaker.undo(Originator).
    Observable
    An observable class will be observed by a list of Observers that will wait for this to notify them.
